      "content": "it really does. it's like... if you knew a building was going to collapse in ten minutes, you wouldn't bother trying to fix the plumbing or making friends with the neighbors. you'd just want to find a way to get out early. i feel like there's no point in just sitting here waiting for the impact. it would be so much more peaceful to just not be part of it anymore.",
